{"tid":1529612,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好對藍絲有任何同情","createTime":"2019-09-01T18:47:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T07:45:33.000Z","uid":90340,"like":106,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"e9a1b2e711c6a762ad0c857e5c2a27f753978d6f","tid":1529612,"uid":90340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T18:47:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/94802341615/posts/10156542185331616?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F94802341615%2Fposts%2F10156542185331616%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=c1rUz8TxCzzDRK4zYpKqdNLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=2370d500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/94802341615/posts/10156542185331616?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OmgCGi4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOmgCGi4.jpg&h=950dc137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家唔值得為呢班自私自利、陰毒賤格嘅人犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qYONi5Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqYONi5Q.jpg&h=bad09865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好記得呢個藍絲呀叔開頭扮好心咁⋯結果係幫黑警手拉手足⋯手足仲要頭落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求你地小心，警惕身邊嘅人，留意周圍環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚多藍絲廢老同便衣潛伏係周圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果受到攻擊的話要還手保衛自己，唔好報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec6c3df2a28820386833ca701944e1cb64ce8d5","tid":1529612,"uid":90340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T18:47:33.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"03a889e922e1705d31ed52d3df2e18bdcea2b55f","tid":1529612,"uid"